headline: Oneok price target lowered to $91 from $94 at Stifel
summary: Stifel lowered the firm’s price target on Oneok (OKE) to $91 from $94 and keeps a Buy rating on the shares. headline: ONEOK Redefines Itself As Multi Commodity Player For AI Energy Demand
summary: ONEOK (NYSE:OKE) is reshaping itself into a diversified infrastructure company, expanding well beyond its roots in natural gas liquids. The company is building out multi-commodity assets while targeting the growing energy needs of large AI focused data centers. Recent integration of major acquisitions and execution on cost and balance sheet goals are central to this transformation story. For investors watching NYSE:OKE, the shift is happening at a time when the stock trades around $82.28...
